Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest evidence

evidence

Purpose:
  Return source-backed evidence for one Wiki Graph object.

Usage:
  spinedigest evidence <archive.sdpub> <uri> [--json|--jsonl] [--help|-h]

Examples:
  spinedigest evidence book.sdpub wikigraph://entity/Q162593
  spinedigest evidence book.sdpub wikigraph://triple/Q162593/discusses/Q9476
